pull_request.title: Introduce common coeff_signed_to_unsigned function in poly.c
pull_request.body: This PR introduces a common "coeff_signed_to_unsigned()" function in poly.c, its contracts and verification thereof using CBMC. This function reduces repetition of the same idiom in poly.c and simplifies the calling code in poly_compress() and other functions.
